        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/theark/scene_magpie.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository deb93f61-a6c2-4691-8524-1353510483c4).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Both of your targets for tonight are survivors of the GAMA Outbreak, an event I&apos;m sure you&apos;re well aquainted with. Fueled with curiousity about the deadly virus, the two entered a business partnership to recreate the virus for their own personal gain. The project gained the interest of Zoe Washington, who agree to provide executive roles in the Ark Society in exchange for acess to the research. Tonight, they come out of hiding at the annual Ark gathering. Happy hunting, 47.",
